items.Video_Title: Is WEEKDAY The Best For Affordable Basics?
items.Video_Description:
So, to carry on my series of looking for the best basics out there, I’m going to be reviewing Weekday today. I have picked up a load of stuff from the brand and I’m going to talk about what I like about them and what I don’t like.

If you didn't know who Weekday are, they are a Swedish brand, owned by H&M. They offer basic clothing at an affordable price and they are very popular these days.
